Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Brno, South Moravia, March 24 (CTK) -- Two Brno men 
who last week attempted to sell 1.024 kilogram of heroin to a 
Dutch citizen have been charged with the unlawful production and 
possession of opiates and psychotropic substances, the district 
investigation office told CTK today. 
