<F P=100> WEST EUROPE </F>
<F P=101> DENMARK </F>
<H3> <TI>   Number of Drug Users in Ringkobing County Has Quadrupled Since 1988 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WD0235D Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 12 Feb 94 
p 2 </F>

<F P=103> 94WD0235D </F>
<F P=104>  Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Danish </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Unattributed article: `More Drug Users in Ringkobing </F>
County'] 
  [Text] New statistics for the counties show that the number 
of drug users in Ringkobing County has quadrupled since 1988. 
Currently the county has contact with 271 needle users and users 
with serious mixed-use problems. In contrast, the number of drug 
users in Viborg County has remained comparatively stable, the 
radio station for the midlands and western region reported. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-22092 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "jptdd013__l94095" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   JPRS-tdd-94-013-L </AU>
Document Type:JPRS 
Document Title:Narcotics 

<DATE1>  7 February 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> WEST EUROPE </F>
<F P=101> DENMARK </F>
<H3> <TI>   Pair Sentenced for Smuggling 85 Kg of Hashish to Norway </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94WD0235F Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 7 Feb 94 p 
3 </F>

