<DOCNO> FBIS3-22308 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "jpten007___94035" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   JPRS-TEN-94-007 </AU>
Document Type:JPRS 
Document Title:Environmental Issues 

<DATE1>  23 February 1994 </DATE1>

